// Detune — désaccordage progressif
// Démo : [detune:N] en cents (100 cents = 1 demi-ton)

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser
@mm:80

S -> D0 D15 D30 D50 D100 End

D0 -> [wave:sawtooth, vel:80, detune:0] C3 E3 G3
D15 -> [detune:15] C3 E3 G3
D30 -> [detune:30] C3 E3 G3
D50 -> [detune:50] C3 E3 G3
D100 -> [detune:100] C3 E3 G3
End -> [detune:0] C3 _ _
